About Rockland Luggage Since its inception in 1998, Rockland by Fox Luggage has been proudly producing quality luggage and bags for the style savvy traveler. Recognized for its graphic and colorful designs, Rockland prides itself on creating products influenced by current trends in design and fashion. Our products turn heads in a crowd and stand out in the baggage carousel, making it easy for quick exits out the airport. Affordable and travel resistant, Rockland bags are an ideal companion for everything from quick trips to the gym to overnight getaways to extended vacations. Our selection includes: luggage sets (4 piece, 3 piece or 2 piece), hard cases, soft cases, carry ons, rolling backpacks, travel duffels, rolling duffels, cosmetic bags, and kids' backpacks. Over the years, a few Rockland products have been featured in film and television. Their colorful designs make them ideal for an eye catching visual element on screen.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 26, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars LOVE this bag wow!
reviews.reviewText: I can’t believe the quality for the price!! It fit so much stuff! I’d would confidently say you could easily get away with a weeks worth of clothing in this suitcase especially if you put your toiletries in your personal item.I love the zip compartments on this, being able to separate shoes from clothing is just king honestly. I know it’s advertised to use the bungee side for clothes but I found that using the zipped side gives extra space to compress the clothing without harm.The wheels are super glidey and I moved around the airport with ease! The handle has two height settings which I loved but it is a tad wobbly on mine. Not sure if the are all like that but something to note.All in all the quality is fantastic, especially for the price. Would buy again.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 24, 2023
reviews.reviewText: This is a great carry-on suitcase. Love the grey/silver color and it is just the right size. The wheels spin 360° makes it very easy to hustle through the airport. It was not too heavy and I was able to fit quite a bit into it. I got my husband a matching color for our trip to Greece and we were very satisfied with the durability of this as well.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 24, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars BEST PURCHASE IN A LONG TIME!
reviews.reviewText: I shop on Amazon ALL the time and don’t write many reviews… but this luggage deserves it! And I am not getting any discount or free stuff. Just a normal mom who hates shopping, so Amazon is my go-to. I swear!!!Bought 4 of these for a recent trip - one for me, hubby, and 2 sons (9 and 10 yrs). Can’t give this enough positive feedback. We carried on plane without any additional charge and neither airline batted an eye or even thought about checking size. We went to Chicago for fall break. Got there much earlier than our AirBNB was ready, so we wheeled ALL OVER our first day. Then on our last day there, we wheeled to several places and left at coat checks before trekking back around the city and to airport. Not a single issue! We easy wheeled them 5+ miles on this one trip. Holds TONS of stuff and easy to keep organized with the zipper closures on one side for loose/smaller items and pockets for shoes. When home, I put a couple inches of very hot water and some bleach in the bathtub and rolled them around for a minute to clean the wheels and wiped the outside with a Clorox wipe and they are good as like new. We have already gotten our money's worth. You won't be disappointed!!! So easy to pull or push, even for the boys. And very light weight - I have multiple back issues that are agonizing and this thing is lighter than my purse before packed.I’d buy more today without hesitation! By the time we got to the AirBNB my husband was commenting on how great they were and well worth the money!!!! The variety of colors is great. All four of us had different colors, so no confusion about which belongs to who.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 23, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars So far so good…
reviews.reviewText: Bought this for my daughter for her 10th birthday! It was a huge hit! She loves the colors, loves that it’s easy to maneuver, and loves all the space inside!The only two problems I find with it (and reason for 4 stars) is that the handle seems a little flimsy, As other customers have mentioned in their comments. And the material inside with the zipper seems like it may not hold up as well as other luggage. Only time will tell.Would I recommend to friends, yes!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 10, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Exceeded my expectations
reviews.reviewText: I was really impressed with this carry on when it arrived, but I waited until I'd taken a trip to write this review.Pros: great value, sturdy, fit easily in different sized overhead bins, and I was able to pack for 3 days, no problem. I read some mildly negative reviews about the zippers, but I had no concerns. Maybe just pay attention and don't try to overstuff it. I checked it as well, and all I can say is it survived, no problems.Cons: the dimensions make it a tiny bit top heavy walking fast or on carpet. This is super nitpicky, but noticeable. I think if you were really rushing, you'd want to pull it behind you.Overall: after 1 trip, highly recommend!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 12, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Solid suitcases for the price
reviews.reviewText: For the price, there is nothing to complain about. Took this set on a month long trip across the world and they absolutely held up and move nicely. Some of the zippers seem to be fraying but you could attribute that to my overpacking. No cracks, good amount of compartments, durable handles, smooth wheels, no complaints

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 12, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Good value for the money, lightweight and nice color combo
reviews.reviewText: Just used the luggage for travel and had no issues with the zippers, wheels or telescoping handle. It's a good size for carry-on, fits in the overhead compartment, lightweight and comes in a nice color combination (chose mint). Would recommend for the price (got a return at the Amazon warehouse at a good discount).

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 24, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Be aware of two issues and you’re golden
reviews.reviewText: This is a cute carryon that I enjoy using. Its inside features (pockets, etc) help keep me organized.Be aware of two issues right away.1) NEVER check this bag. It will get damaged. It won’t stand up to being squished by all those hulking big bags.2) GENTLY use the zipper. It’s not industrial strength. C’mon, it’s a Barbie-pink bag! Don’t overstuff it. If it’s tight, reorganize so you don’t have a bulging bag. And use that expansion zipper to release pressure.I love it but recognize its shortcomings.
Son muy bonitas, ligeras, sus ruedas van bien, aunque se rayan muy rápido por el manejo de los aeropuertos.

Bought for my 8 & 6 year old. Light enough for them to carry but durable enough to withhold a lot of use. The wheels have held up to the constant use as well. Not to mention the adorable colors. Would highly recommend.

reviews.reviewTitle: Excelente equipaje, variación en el color.
reviews.reviewText: Me encanto el material, los compartimentos y por dentro te trae un pequeño candado para la maleta. Pero el color si es muy diferente al de la imagen yo pedí el color champagne y pensé que sería un color más dorado obscuro como se ve en la foto pero es un rose gold claro. Solo tenerlo en mente por si quieres esa opción de color, de ahí el equipaje es bastante bonito y de calidad.
